  <note> 
   <p>To learn in-depth about creating channels and displays, see <a href="../../screens/using/managing-channels.md">Managing Channels</a> and <a href="/sites/authoring/using/managing-displays">Managing Displays</a> respectively in Authoring Screens.</p> 
